-----------------------------
TkCommissioner for CC7 at P5
-----------------------------

This is the updated version of the TkCommissioner tool used for the commissioning of the CMS silicon strip tracker.

###### Installation procedure

Prerequisites:

       sudo yum install qt.x86_64
       sudo yum install qt-devel.x86_64
       sudo yum install root.x86_64
       sudo yum install root-gui-qt.x86_64
       sudo yum install qt-mysql.x86_64
	
Temporary hack: no QT drivers for Oracle OCI are available in the standard RPMs, therefore they are copied by hand from the older release of tkCommissioner
	
       sudo scp /opt/cmssw/shifter/avartak/qtRoot/qt-everywhere-opensource-src-4.8.2/plugins/sqldrivers/libqsqloci.so /usr/lib64/qt4/plugins/sqldrivers/ 
       sudo scp /opt/xdaq/lib/libclntsh.so.12.1 /opt/xdaq/lib/libclntsh.so.11.1

Download and compile tkCommissioner:
       git clone git@github.com:trackerpro/TkCommissioner.git -b newCommissioner_cc7_developments 
       qmake-qt4
       make		
